力政策+当日新闻+明显超预期\n- **70-84分**：清晰行业指向+重要政策/技术+近期新闻+一定超预期\n- **60-69分**：可推断行业+一般性政策/技术+时效一般+符合预期\n- **40-59分**：行业模糊+影响有限+时效较差+预期之内\n- **0-39分**：多重负面因素叠加，基本无驱动力\n\n## 📥 输入数据\n[{"id": "6902f1b176848c48b898d6d6", "content": "Trump cuts fentanyl tariffs on China to 10%, says U.S. reached rare earths deal with Beijing"}, {"id": "6902f1b276848c48b898d6d7", "content": "26 MIN AGO South Korea’s Hybe adds $644 million in market value after court ruling on K-pop group NewJeans"}, {"id": "6902f1b276848c48b898d6d8", "content": "32 MIN AGO Bank of Japan holds rates in first meeting after Takaichi’s ascent to prime minister"}, {"id": "6902f1b276848c48b898d6d9", "content": "13 MIN AGO Hong Kong and China markets little changed as Trump-Xi meeting concludes"}, {"id": "6902f1b276848c48b898d6da", "content": "6 HOURS AGO Stock futures move lower after tech earnings put focus back on AI trade"}, {"id": "6902f1b276848c48b898d6db", "content": "4 HOURS AGO South Korean markets smash records as investors bet on AI and corporate governance reforms"}, {"id": "6902f1b276848c48b898d6dc", "content": "4 HOURS AGO Capex is the number to look at amid Big Tech earnings"}, {"id": "6902f1ba76848c48b898d6dd", "content": "22 MIN AGO ‘Partners and friends’: Xi strikes conciliatory tone as he meets Trump in South Korea"}, {"id": "6902f1ba76848c48b898d6de", "content": "43 MIN AGO Chinese companies have begun to dominate Southeast Asia’s online shopping market"}, {"id": "6902f1d476848c48b898d6df", "content": "Reuters\\n•\\n18m ago Instant View: Market analysts react to Trump-Xi meeting"}, {"id": "6902f1d476848c48b898d6e0", "content": "Reuters\\n•\\n30m ago Travel tech firm Navan\'s IPO raises about $923 million"}, {"id": "6902f1d476848c48b898d6e1", "content": "Reuters\\n•\\n32m ago Market analysts react to Trump-Xi meeting"}, {"id": "6902f1d476848c48b898d6e2", "content": "Reuters\\n•\\n36m ago South Korea releases details of trade deal struck with the US"}, {"id": "6902f1d476848c48b898d6e3", "content": "Reute